Package: scRATE
Type: Package
Title: A scRNA-seq quantification toolkit based on Bayesian model selection
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Kwangbom "KB" Choi, Ph.D.
Maintainer: Kwangbom "KB" Choi, Ph.D. <kb.choi@jax.org>
Description: Estimate gene expression rate using the best model to which count data conforms.
    Performs model selection based on posterior predictive checks.
